===Dedicated satellite channels===
[[File:Prisavlje.JPG|right|thumb|[[Satellite dish]]es at the [[Croatian Radiotelevision|HRT]] building in Zagreb|alt=Light-colored satellite dishes on the HRT building in Zagreb]]
HRT broadcasts dedicated satellite channels for Europe and the Middle East, [[North America|North]] and South America, Australia and New Zealand; viewing the channels requires a subscription.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Croatian Radiotelevision|url=http://www.hrt.hr/index.php?id=186&tx_ttnews%5Bcat%5D=126&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=1787&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=185&cHash=ac69c865cd|title=HRT broadcasting via satellite|accessdate=1 January 2012}}</ref> Channels broadcast to Europe and the Middle East via the [[Hot Bird]] 6 satellite (using [[Viaccess]] [[conditional access]]) are HTV1, HTV2 and HRT PLUS. The satellite channels are also used to transmit three [[free-to-air]] radio channels produced by HRT.<ref name="HRT-HB6">{{cite web|publisher=Croatian Radiotelevision|title=Broadcasting via satellite for Europe and Middle East|url=http://www.hrt.hr/index.php?id=186&tx_ttnews%5Bcat%5D=126&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=1792&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=185&cHash=482afd3d6b|date=1 January 2012}}</ref> North America, Australia and New Zealand receive the [[Slika Hrvatske]] (Picture of Croatia) channel via the [[Galaxy 19]] (North America) and the [[Optus (satellite)|Optus D2]] (Australia and New Zealand) satellites. The broadcast are encrypted using [[Irdeto]] 2 conditional access.<ref name="HRT-OptD2">{{cite web|publisher=Croatian Radiotelevision|title=Broadcasting HRT programmes via satellite for Australia and New Zealand |url=http://www.hrt.hr/index.php?id=186&tx_ttnews%5Bcat%5D=126&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=1793&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=185&cHash=4d25942a86|date=1 January 2012}}</ref><ref name="HRT-Gal19">{{cite web|publisher=Croatian Radiotelevision|title=Broadcasting HRT programmes via satellite for North America |url=http://www.hrt.hr/index.php?id=186&tx_ttnews%5Bcat%5D=126&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=131664&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=185&cHash=e3701d8971|date=1 January 2012}}</ref>

